Package ws.rocket.config.section.write

Contract and implementations for writing a configuration section data to target bean.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SectionWriter
    A section writer determines how the data collected by section reader is to be written to target beam.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BeanConstructorWriter
    An advanced section data writer that determines the property type, and creates an instance of it by calling the constructor with as many parameters as given to this class.
    BeanConstructPropertyWriter
    An advanced section data writer that determines the property type, and creates an instance of it by calling the constructor with as many parameters as given to this class.
    MultiPropertyWriter
    A section data writer that writes each value to corresponding property of target bean.
    SimplePropertyWriter
    A section data writer that will store the received collection in a property of the target bean.
